cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper discusses the use of deep convolutional networks for action recognition in videos, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the challenges of training very deep networks and proposes good practices for training, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of the Caffe toolbox for implementation, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper discusses the small size of the training dataset and the potential for overfitting, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
